{"tid":2189373,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"London Bridge冇窗地牢招租 每月£2,000","createTime":"2020-09-05T00:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T12:34:49.000Z","uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"953c4c7b05a4b9c7f40fad75b81e1c9e84575a78","tid":2189373,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T00:05:57.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">Rental Opportunity of the Week: A Remodelled Crypt, for Goths<br />\nYour own windowless basement in London Bridge, for just &pound;2,000 a month.</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">By Joel Golby</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://video-images.vice.com//articles/5f4fcfd46bd888009a8555c7/lede/1599069647010-lrotw-thumb.png?crop=1xw:0.8425xh;0xw,0.1284xh&amp;resize=500:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo-images.vice.com%2F%2Farticles%2F5f4fcfd46bd888009a8555c7%2Flede%2F1599069647010-lrotw-thumb.png%3Fcrop%3D1xw%3A0.8425xh%3B0xw%2C0.1284xh%26resize%3D500%3A%2A&h=388fb19d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">PHOTOS VIA RIGHT MOVE</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">What is it?</span></strong> <br />\nI don&rsquo;t know the difference between a dungeon and a crypt &ndash; and I do feel like knowing the fine-texture differences between those things earns you placement on some sort of database, a goth terror watchlist that encompasses &ldquo;everyone who ever subscribed to Bizarre Magazine&rdquo;, &ldquo;every UK-based taxidermy forum user&rdquo; and &ldquo;people who know what the difference between dungeons and crypts is&rdquo;, and every time any one of them leaves the house in a leather trench coat that goes beyond the knee they get silently trailed by plainclothes &ndash; but let&rsquo;s split the difference and say &ldquo;a dungeon and/or crypt&rdquo;.<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">Where is it?</span></strong> <br />\nIn London Bridge, home of the Shard, a big train station with an understocked M&amp;S, and absolutely fuck all else.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://video-images.vice.com/_uncategorized/1599069988815-50683p237123img010000.jpeg?resize=800:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo-images.vice.com%2F_uncategorized%2F1599069988815-50683p237123img010000.jpeg%3Fresize%3D800%3A%2A&h=cf40f8f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://video-images.vice.com/_uncategorized/1599070050780-50683p237123img020000.jpeg?resize=800:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo-images.vice.com%2F_uncategorized%2F1599070050780-50683p237123img020000.jpeg%3Fresize%3D800%3A%2A&h=76f0bb68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://video-images.vice.com/_uncategorized/1599070067548-50683p237123img030000.jpeg?resize=800:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo-images.vice.com%2F_uncategorized%2F1599070067548-50683p237123img030000.jpeg%3Fresize%3D800%3A%2A&h=98af16c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://video-images.vice.com/_uncategorized/1599070118227-50683p237123img040000.jpeg?resize=800:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo-images.vice.com%2F_uncategorized%2F1599070118227-50683p237123img040000.jpeg%3Fresize%3D800%3A%2A&h=c066f0de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://video-images.vice.com/_uncategorized/1599070099453-50683p237123img090000.jpeg?resize=800:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo-images.vice.com%2F_uncategorized%2F1599070099453-50683p237123img090000.jpeg%3Fresize%3D800%3A%2A&h=277dc239&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.vice.com/en_uk/article/akz9ze/rental-opportunity-london-bridge-basement?fbclid=IwAR3heFBcu0tzMsAB6U42MZxFhl_ESQKwA5ZIAjTuPi4rl7H_BsMsGkmlnls\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vice.com%2Fen_uk%2Farticle%2Fakz9ze%2Frental-opportunity-london-bridge-basement%3F